{"tid":247260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洗完澡出來，發現渡邊麻友躺在我床上","createTime":"2017-05-17T15:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T03:44:26.000Z","uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"676f55033c45c96a2769b9c79b55c6e2234a1208","tid":247260,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"AKB48人氣成員渡邊麻友睽違5年，日前於10月25日推出第二本個人寫真集「不知不覺中」（知らないうちに），甫推出就拿下該周銷售冠軍，證明AKB48老將的價值。不過正所謂人紅是非多，24日日本搞笑藝人村本大輔最新PO文居然寫說，「渡邊麻友躺在我床上。」究竟是怎麼回事呢？<br />\n<br />\n村本大輔是搞笑團體「Woman Rush Hour」成員之一是個以調戲女藝人當賣點的渣男。不過就算再怎麼嘴，把到我們肥宅中的女神，還把她脫光光放床上拍照上網炫耀（嗯...這句話好多動詞，大概會被罵了），也太過份了吧。<br />\n<br />\n▼村本大輔寫說渡邊麻友如何誘惑他全文，「你洗澡洗好久阿，快點來睡覺吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/2171719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2F2171719.jpg&h=aae4e9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/2171720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2F2171720.jpg&h=8c26ce17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/2171723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2F2171723.jpg&h=02a9c9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來只是寫真啊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/2171724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2F2171724.jpg&h=086cc0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞半天即使厲害如村本大輔，有機會和渡邊麻友一起共事，還是只能用這種肥宅方式意淫啊。<br />\n<br />\n好吧，你淫了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/2171721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2F2171721.jpg&h=408cce89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果這樣也行，那派大星今晚也能和各位酸酸們預告，「大島優子在我床上！如何？羨慕吧？」（嗚嗚嗚，明明很幸福，可是不知道為什麼，淚水止不住阿。）"},{"pid":"f3984f6a794ab50709c23d063562f06cf6eaadd8","tid":247260,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"98447a920e34366d90e8411da1a2f30288c7c61f","tid":247260,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>g<del>ood</del></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2704973bed4c2649e54cb3ed7909b2fd33c8a644","tid":247260,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"打柒佢"},{"pid":"6a42fac21424e3493c4da02c3d3781090cbc254f","tid":247260,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"Ching醒醒"},{"pid":"ad048a31a367de249aeee68c7630f9c64d6ccae1","tid":247260,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"41d6a07d5273467b1273de10471b0a21ccc5b50d","tid":247260,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"非法入屋罪<br />\n報警啦屌"},{"pid":"4eefd96d869fcca8332519035948fcede1836e91","tid":247260,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"「你洗澡洗好久阿，快點來睡覺吧。」"},{"pid":"a8d201e86beb07cd3fa6ebb13603e03d65dabf7d","tid":247260,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602e6117c380730794fc1177897f28473f91b9bc","tid":247260,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:44:26.000Z","msg":"mayuyu"}]}